"{\"uid\": \"thegatewaypundit.com-2024-07-no-shame-olympic-organizers-issue-pathetic-apology-cruelly\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  As The Gateway Punditreported, the Paris Olympic organizers allowed a reenactment of The Last Supper with drag queens during the 2024 Olympics ceremony.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 154, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the sickening opening ceremony, the scantily dressed drag queens stood behind a long table while mocking one of the most sacred images in all of Christianity.\", \"from\": 156, \"to\": 317, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 304, \"end\": 316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9972992896944809, \"rank\": 0.002704709766222688, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Worse, a young child was also spotted standing beside the drag queens in the performance.\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 407, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, ESPNreportsthat the Olympic committee is scrambling to contain the fallout.\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 489, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On Sunday morning, Paris 2024 spokesperson Anne Descamps issued a so-called 'apology' if anyone was offended by the sick performance while maintaining they managed to celebrate \\\"community tolerance.\\\"\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 689, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 509, \"end\": 519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 2.3649100147774994e-13, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 538, \"end\": 546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Clearly, there was never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group.\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 772, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It (The opening ceremony) tried to celebrate community tolerance,\\\" Descamps claimed during a news conference.\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 840, \"end\": 848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We believe this ambition was achieved,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 935, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If people have taken any offense, we are really sorry.\\\"\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 992, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Translation: we have no regrets over the performance, and it's your fault for misinterpreting our intentions, silly Christians.\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1110, \"end\": 1120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"score\": 0.652711408759031, \"rank\": 0.5192934544669469, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Christians worldwide remain livid that their faith was insulted at an event that is supposed to emphasize unity.\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1246, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1134, \"end\": 1144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"score\": 0.652711408759031, \"rank\": 0.5192934544669469, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Daily Mail notes that THOUSANDS of Olympic fans have now vowed not to watch the event.\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1337, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1251, \"end\": 1261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Mail\", \"score\": 0.9999999999859028, \"rank\": 1.4035463177592623e-11, \"text\": \"Daily Mail\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Mail\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Mail\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hashtags #boycottOlympics and #boycottParis2024 trended globally Saturday and have continued intoSunday.\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1443, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thisfollowsone of the largest telecommunications providers in the United States yanking ads following the blasphemous performance.\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1511, \"end\": 1524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999329549271222, \"rank\": 6.704884744912625e-05, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From the DailyMail:  Thousands of social media users have threatened to boycott the nascent Paris Olympics after its opening ceremony was widely panned on Friday.\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1739, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1669, \"end\": 1683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Enraged viewers took to X where #boycottOlympics and #boycottParis2024 were seen trending over the course of the following day.\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1868, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In particular, the appearance of a 'naked blue man' among a scene likened to the Last Supper angered many watching, especially Christians.\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 2008, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1997, \"end\": 2007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"score\": 0.652711408759031, \"rank\": 0.5192934544669469, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You canemail Cullen Linebarger here, andread more of Cullen Linebarger's articles here.\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2097, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2023, \"end\": 2029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Cullen\", \"score\": 0.9902640788222357, \"rank\": 0.00980895474019774, \"text\": \"Cullen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Cullen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Cullen\"}, {\"begin\": 2063, \"end\": 2069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Cullen\", \"score\": 0.9902640788222357, \"rank\": 0.00980895474019774, \"text\": \"Cullen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Cullen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Cullen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign up now and stay ahead in the political landscape.\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2155, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"VisitGatewayHispanic.comto read news of interest to the hispanic community.\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2232, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2213, \"end\": 2221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hispanic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"hispanic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hispanic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hispanic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"VisitAmericanGulag.orgto learn how to help the prisoners of the protest on January 6th.\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2321, \"ent